00:36:14,884 --> 00:36:19,184
-What kind of gun do you use?
-G-3, rifles,

547
00:36:19,389 --> 00:36:21,482
<i>CARLINHOS 16 YEARS OLD
9 mm pistols, .45,</i>

548
00:36:21,691 --> 00:36:25,491
<i>PT, .38 caliber... It depends
on the guns they give us.</i>

549
00:36:27,130 --> 00:36:30,566
<i>Today,Rio de Janeiro
dealers use AK-47,</i>

550
00:36:30,767 --> 00:36:34,703
<i>which is Russian,
it's a guerrilla rifle.</i>

551
00:36:34,904 --> 00:36:38,931
<i>They use AR-15, grenades,
rocket launchers...</i>

552
00:36:39,142 --> 00:36:44,705
<i>Recently, we've noticed they're
using night vision equipment,</i>

553
00:36:44,914 --> 00:36:47,849
<i>something even
our platoon doesn't have.</i>

554
00:36:48,151 --> 00:36:49,778
POLICE WAREHOUSE FOR
CONFISCATED WEAPONS

555
00:37:10,540 --> 00:37:13,703
<i>When it comes to drug dealing,
we must mention gun smuggling.</i>

556
00:37:13,910 --> 00:37:18,074
The profit from drugs
and gun selling are related.

557
00:37:18,281 --> 00:37:20,442
Look at the guns they make
by the end of the century.

558
00:37:20,650 --> 00:37:23,744
Why produce a rifle
that shoots 700 bullets a minute

559
00:37:23,953 --> 00:37:26,353
by the end of the century?
Isn't the Berlin Wall down?

560
00:37:26,556 --> 00:37:30,788
What 's the issue?
Are there frontiers

561
00:37:30,994 --> 00:37:33,554
to be drawn?

562
00:37:33,763 --> 00:37:36,823
There is no real interest in this.
Then, why do they make those?

563
00:37:37,300 --> 00:37:43,899
<i>The gun made in Switzerland
won't be sold in Libya, will it?</i>

564
00:37:44,107 --> 00:37:47,599
