568
00:37:59,823 --> 00:38:01,916
Because they can sell it
for the highest price.

569
00:38:02,058 --> 00:38:07,086
OK, then. We have to close
gun factories in Switzerland,

570
00:38:07,297 --> 00:38:09,993
<i>in the US... Colt is American,
and the AR-15 is made by Colt.</i>

571
00:38:10,200 --> 00:38:12,361
I want to close Colt 's factory.

572
00:38:12,735 --> 00:38:15,863
This is how they handle
The drug war,

573
00:38:16,072 --> 00:38:18,336
and I thing it's fair.
It should be the same for us.

574
00:38:18,541 --> 00:38:20,839
They want to interfere in Colombia.

575
00:38:21,044 --> 00:38:24,207
They come into plantations,
and they want to control production

576
00:38:24,414 --> 00:38:28,350
in Colombia and in Peru. I want to
have control, to close Colt, in the US,

577
00:38:28,551 --> 00:38:31,884
and Sig-Sauer, in Switzerland.
What is the real issue?

578
00:38:37,927 --> 00:38:40,487
<i>There are favelas
with 100 armed men.</i>

579
00:38:40,697 --> 00:38:44,189
<i>They carry sophisticated armament.</i>

580
00:38:44,834 --> 00:38:47,302
The day they realize
the status quo,

581
00:38:47,503 --> 00:38:50,631
and they decide to come
down in an organized manner,

582
00:38:50,840 --> 00:38:52,535
they'll take over.

583
00:38:58,448 --> 00:39:00,507
DISRUPTION

