601
00:40:05,148 --> 00:40:07,013
<i>KILLED IN JUNE, 94.
Some people died</i>

602
00:40:07,216 --> 00:40:10,014
<i>in their first mission.</i>

603
00:40:10,219 --> 00:40:12,153
<i>KILLED IN AUGUST, 87.
Others were arrested. The whole</i>

604
00:40:12,355 --> 00:40:14,084
thing fell apart.
