664
00:43:38,828 --> 00:43:42,286
They might help people,
but they don't have the structure

665
00:43:42,498 --> 00:43:46,525
to replace the State.
This is a lie.

666
00:43:48,371 --> 00:43:53,138
There might be some kind
of rudimentary structure.

667
00:43:55,111 --> 00:43:59,377
<i>They're stupid.
Uê stayed in 5-star hotels.</i>

668
00:43:59,749 --> 00:44:02,912
It's stupid! Is there anything
easier than catching Uê

669
00:44:03,119 --> 00:44:04,211
at a 5-star hotel?
It's stupid.

670
00:44:04,420 --> 00:44:08,379
He could stay in a 3-star
hotel and remain unnoticed.

671
00:44:08,591 --> 00:44:13,893
He goes to a 5-star hotel.
We don't even have to ask who he is.

672
00:44:14,096 --> 00:44:18,760
This is the deal.
It's chaos. We live in chaos here.

673
00:44:18,968 --> 00:44:22,335
<i>15-year-old kids have no
