00:44:24,240 --> 00:44:30,201
<i>It's a crazy situation.
Kids with Sig-Sauers, AR-15...</i>

676
00:44:32,114 --> 00:44:34,139
CHAOS

677
00:44:35,885 --> 00:44:37,944
The dealer is escaping
through the window!

678
00:44:38,154 --> 00:44:39,712
MANCHETE TV STOCKSHOT
The police keeps shooting!

679
00:44:39,922 --> 00:44:44,655
There's another dealer trying to
escape. He's gonna jump! Look!

680
00:45:25,568 --> 00:45:28,560
<i>You put the squeeze on this
favela and they go to the next.</i>

681
00:45:28,771 --> 00:45:33,401
<i>You go to the next, they move
again. It's an endless war.</i>

682
00:45:33,609 --> 00:45:36,510
Even if you go over...
For 2 weeks,

683
00:45:36,712 --> 00:45:39,943
almost every night, the BOPE
would kill a dealer over there.

684
00:45:40,149 --> 00:45:43,676
It'd confiscate a pistol
or a rifle and kill a dealer.

685
00:45:43,886 --> 00:45:48,084
Did it solve a thing?
It didn't. It didn't solve anything.

686
00:45:48,791 --> 00:45:51,055
<i>For the young people there...</i>

687
00:45:51,260 --> 00:45:54,058
<i>There are dozens of young
men who are not part of it,</i>

688
00:45:54,263 --> 00:45:57,198
<i>but are waiting in line
to get in on it.</i>

689
00:45:58,134 --> 00:46:03,834
Maybe, the new leader,
because he's even younger...

690
00:46:04,040 --> 00:46:05,507
<i>We have just witnessed
the formation</i>

691
00:46:05,708 --> 00:46:07,938
<i>of the youth's organization,
Comando Vermelho Jovem, CVJ.</i>

692
00:46:08,644 --> 00:46:12,205
<i>Being younger, they are
even more prone to violence.</i>

693
00:46:17,353 --> 00:46:20,049
If we have a shoot-out
with the police,

694
00:46:20,256 --> 00:46:24,158
many times they back away
and leave 1 or 2 soldiers behind.

695
00:46:24,360 --> 00:46:27,727
If we get the soldier,
we tie him up, beat him,

696
00:46:27,930 --> 00:46:30,592
shoot him, put him in
a barrel and set fire to it.

697
00:46:35,104 --> 00:46:37,732
When did you get into this life?

698
00:46:38,240 --> 00:46:41,107
When I was 11 years old.

699
00:46:41,510 --> 00:46:43,478
What was your 1st mission?

700
00:46:43,679 --> 00:46:47,206
My first mission was
to kill an informant.

701
00:46:47,883 --> 00:46:49,942
At 11 years old...

702
00:46:50,152 --> 00:46:51,710
What did he do?
What did you do?

703
00:46:51,921 --> 00:46:56,358
He told the police we pack
cocaine and marihuana.

704
00:46:56,559 --> 00:46:58,550
He told it to the ''worms'',
the policemen.

705
00:46:58,894 --> 00:47:00,327
Then, I set him on fire.

706
00:47:00,529 --> 00:47:04,295
I got 7 car tires,

707
00:47:04,500 --> 00:47:05,797
I mean, 7 truck tires.

708
00:47:06,001 --> 00:47:08,993
I got 5 liters of gasoline.

709
00:47:09,238 --> 00:47:12,002
I lit a match
and set him on fire.

710
00:47:12,208 --> 00:47:13,937
Who asked you to do that?

711
00:47:14,143 --> 00:47:16,771
It was my boss.

712
00:47:17,546 --> 00:47:20,106
How did you feel
after doing that?

713
00:47:20,316 --> 00:47:23,945
I felt normal,
like I feel right now.

714
00:47:24,420 --> 00:47:27,253
If I have to kill again,
I'll do it.

715
00:47:28,257 --> 00:47:30,725
When I kill?

716
00:47:30,960 --> 00:47:35,090
The only feeling I have is
that I've fulfilled my duty.

717
00:47:35,297 --> 00:47:37,891
If I say I got home
and couldn't sleep, I'd be lying.

718
00:47:38,300 --> 00:47:39,767
Have you ever killed
a policeman?

719
00:47:39,969 --> 00:47:43,496
No, I haven't had
that opportunity.

720
00:47:50,146 --> 00:47:52,376
<i>I stay on a roof at
the top of the favela</i>

721
00:47:52,581 --> 00:47:56,813
with a 9 mm pistol
that has a laser beam.

722
00:47:57,019 --> 00:48:00,978
I point the beam at their
chest or head, and they run.

723
00:48:01,190 --> 00:48:04,091
<i>The beam marks the place
where the bullet will enter.</i>

724
00:48:07,563 --> 00:48:10,726
If it's on your forehead,
the bullet will hit it.

725
00:48:11,066 --> 00:48:13,091
I intend to go back on the streets
and do it all over again.

726
00:48:13,302 --> 00:48:17,500
-This time it will be worst.
-What will you do?

727
00:48:17,706 --> 00:48:20,698
I'll rob more banks,
more armored cars.

728
00:48:20,910 --> 00:48:23,208
I'll raise millions,
and help the needy.

729
00:48:28,184 --> 00:48:31,642
<i>The police fights a personal war.</i>

730
00:48:31,854 --> 00:48:34,721
<i>If we kill a dealer,
other dealers will hate the police.</i>

731
00:48:34,924 --> 00:48:36,755
<i>They kill a policeman,
and then we hate them.</i>

732
00:48:36,959 --> 00:48:41,225
It develops at that level.
The war is almost personal now.

