746
00:49:31,146 --> 00:49:34,775
I used to make money
at the favela.

747
00:49:34,984 --> 00:49:37,976
But what exactly does
a''fireworks kid'' do?

748
00:49:38,187 --> 00:49:41,486
When the ''heat'' came,
I'd use fireworks.

749
00:49:44,326 --> 00:49:46,419
It works just like an alarm.
People have time to hide.

750
00:49:47,963 --> 00:49:50,158
The policemen did this.

751
00:49:50,366 --> 00:49:52,857
I want money for this.

752
00:49:55,437 --> 00:49:58,235
I don't see an end to it.

753
00:49:58,440 --> 00:50:02,240
There's no light
at the end of the tunnel.

754
00:50:02,444 --> 00:50:04,639
I see no solution.

